Package: hubtools
Type: Package
Title: Forecasting Hub Workflow Tools
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Metrocast", "Team", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "metrocast@example.com")
Description: Utilities for data collection, visualization, and evaluation of Forecasting Hub workflows,
    compatible with flu-metrocast and similar hubs. Provides helpers for observed vs forecast plots,
    selection patterns (fix date or fix horizon), multi-model evaluation metrics, and population utilities.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    dplyr,
    tidyr,
    tibble,
    readr,
    ggplot2,
    lubridate,
    stringr,
    purrr,
    rlang,
    magrittr
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
Config/testthat/edition: 3
URL: https://github.com/reichlab/hubtools
BugReports: https://github.com/reichlab/hubtools/issues
